body: ### Paul Reiners' GitHub Projects * [udacity-intro-hadoop-mapreduce](http://paul-reiners.github.io/udacity-intro-hadoop-mapreduce/): Final project for Udacity Introduction to Hadoop and MapReduce course. * [kaggle-the-analytics-edge](http://paul-reiners.github.io/kaggle-the-analytics-edge/): Code for private Kaggle competition held as part of MITx : 15.071x The Analytics Edge course. Illustrates my knowledge of data analytics techniques including random forests and logistic regression. Written in R. * [quadrillionth-decimal-place](http://paul-reiners.github.io/quadrillionth-decimal-place/): Implementation (in C) of a Method of Bailey, Borwein, and Plouffe. * [twisted-life](http://paul-reiners.github.io/twisted-life/): Video game (written in CoffeeScript) based on J.H. Conway's Game of Life. [Play](http://www.automatous-monk.com/twistedlife/) the game.
